&lt;li&gt;ChatGPT vs. the Lawyer: My Aggravating Battle to Get Answers from an AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The AI Witness From Hell: My Frustrating Encounter with ChatGPT&lt;/li&gt;
